<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176354>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1 – 5. Holotype of: 1 Laparocerus aguiari n. sp. 2 Laparocerus boticarius n. sp. 3 Laparocerus chasnensis n. sp. 4 Laparocerus subparallelus n. sp. and 5 Laparocerus tinguaro n. sp. Scale = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176354/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176355>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Laparocerus aguiari n. sp. A. Male genitalia, lateral view. B. Apical end of median lobe in dorsal view. C. Spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176355/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176356>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Laparocerus boticarius n. sp. A. Male genitalia, lateral view. B. Apical end of median lobe in dorsal view. C. Spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176356/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176357>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Laparocerus chasnensis n. sp. A. Male genitalia, lateral view. B. Apical end of median lobe in dorsal view. C. Spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176357/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176358>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Laparocerus subparallelus n. sp. A. Male genitalia, lateral view. B. Apical end of median lobe in dorsal view. C. Spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176358/files/figure.png" ;
